title: Bitwise AND of Numbers Range
description: Given a range [m, n] where 0 <= m <= n <= 2147483647, return the bitwise AND of all numbers in this range, inclusive.
note: For example, given the range [5, 7], you should return 4.

title: Bitwise XOR of Numbers Range
description: Given a range [m, n] where 0 <= m <= n <= 2147483647, return the bitwise XOR of all numbers in this range, inclusive.
note: For example, given the range [5, 7], you should return 4.

title: Happy Number
description: Write an algorithm to determine if a number is "happy".

title: Remove Linked List Elements
description: Remove all elements from a linked list of integers that have value val.
